headline: Rollins Gears Up to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in the Offing?
summary: ROL is set to report fourth-quarter results on Feb. 11, with the consensus calling for 17.4% EPS growth and 10.8% revenue growth driven by Orkin-led demand.
